Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today marks one month since\Nthe subway derailment incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The station where it took place\Nremains out of operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with customer complaints\Ncoming in one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure feel sorry for this CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly was a miracle that it was\Nan unmanned out-of-service train,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,resulting in not even a single casualty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We plan to investigate and address\Nthe cause as swiftly as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so to continue providing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this CEO is completely out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The brave choice we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Its future is being illuminated♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If we clash our selfish emotions\Nwe can't see it (yet)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫To catch up on the distance\Nwe fled from (see) let's go on a journey♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Even if we can't see the farthest lands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We just burn our lives\Nto keep living in the present♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Proof of the existence we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We kept our voices trembling\Nwhile we brandished it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫No need for regret, we go\Nhand in hand (even the dark past)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We accept it and move forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Instead of choosing an answer shown to us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We're aspiring a new dream (always)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Let's walk along the radiant road♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(#05 So far, so good)\NAll right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain our next assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a real fun job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one explaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already read the briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, you there!\N- She's really excited about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut the chatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the squirrel up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing video games?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our client is male, 72 years old, Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His wife and daughter were killed,\Nand with his own life in peril,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he fled to the United States to\Ntake refuge ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He currently has... amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a-amyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amyotrophic lateral sclerosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he can't move on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, he found out\Nhow long he has to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he wanted to have one last look around\Nhis homeland of Japan, and Tokyo to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brings a tear to your eye, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's still\Na chance his life is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll be his bodyguards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they after his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a director of a large corporation,\Nso he's got his share of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pay's real good to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine he'd be in danger\Nso soon after arriving in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'll leave the itinerary up to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll come up with the perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could make a travel guidebook for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I arrive a tad bit early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking forward to this, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, we're ready as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our travel guidebook is immaculate as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, want me to send it over as data?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to these ladies,\Nso you can take your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These machines are what keep me alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you must find that strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a pacemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's completely mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An artificial heart, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there's ice running through that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice and machines don't mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait, what do you...\N- Okay, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(File received)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's embark on our\Nsightseeing tour of Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, what Chisato was just talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki! The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can leave that to Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hardly expected this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumida City is surrounded by several rivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can get around the\Ncity center via water taxi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all without having to worry about traffic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has collapsed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen it before it did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is my first time in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had made a promise with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's look up at it together,\Nuntil our necks start hurting."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell her about it on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that, we've only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The official name for it is "Furaijinmon".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was built in 942 AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you'd expect from its official name,\NRaijin sits to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Fujin to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're deities who protect\NSenso-ji from calamity and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, they're guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me and Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we work just for you, Matsushita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the adorable deities you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This crowd's barely moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shops between Kaminarimon-dori\Nand Senso-ji Kannondo-mae
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are why it's called Nakamise-dori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senso-ji was founded 1,400 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when in Sumida River, where we just were,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fishermen got a Buddhist statue\Ncaught in their net and enshrined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Bodhisattva Kannon\Nworshiped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Kannon will bring\Nsalvation to all living things on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All living things, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not something I could ever hope to imitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check out the five-storied pagoda next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(No Trespassing)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would a train collision really\Ntake down the ceiling like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A bullet?! Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all this as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the other bullets\Nhave already been collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a terrorist attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was no accident!\NI need to let the chief know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This has been covered up as an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the terrorist attack\Non the old radio tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lots of incidents have been\Nrewritten as accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even say whether they're secretly\Nresolving it or just covering it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief's been hiding it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's probably just acting on orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay keeping this quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They manage to cover up everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to take on, ya bonehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're detectives, why are we running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlawful trespassing sure is stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if it isn't Chisato-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you noticed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got good eyesight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina-chan's with you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoying the festival together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of\Na guided tour with a client!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, good luck with your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good kid, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If kids like her can live in peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does it really matter who's covering up what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe an artificial heart\Ncan tolerate so much physical activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have a look\Nat DA's R&D servers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not DA technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean it's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous Alan Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't keep a secret from you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means in exchange for living,\Nshe was given a mission to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Chisato's mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for Chisato to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it'll be finished by November.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An acquaintance of mine is\Ninvolved with its design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's leaving behind something\Nmonumental for future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should come\Nand see it once it's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on another tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I would gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a most wonderful guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is hot out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go get some brief rest inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like he's enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I was a good guide!\NMaybe I've got a knack for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The escort's safety comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true what you said this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised that it doesn't beat,\Nbut this thing's pretty wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but don't touch\Nmy boobs in public like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that's been\Ntailing them for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him Silent Jin from\Nhow quietly he carries out his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently a veteran hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until 15 years ago, the two of us worked\Nthe covert jobs at a security firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was before I was scouted\Nas a Lycoris training instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent... It's true I've\Nnever heard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spotted 30 meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna go plant a transmitter on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't spot him from above.\NWhat about you, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stopped next to a column.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He's onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's a nasty one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll evacuate the target\Nand have one of you go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we find Jin with Mizuki and\Nthe backup drone, you'll go on the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you exit the museum,\NI'll have the car ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything without that drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get your butt\Nover here as backup instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! This creep's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the backup drone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the channel and alert the other two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's about to go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just off to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run the indoor security cam footage\Nthrough facial recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending a backup drone\Nto cover outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can begin analysis 10 minutes from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mizuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio silence after losing\Ncontact 500 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The museum entrance is facing the department\Nstore, so I'll check the museum cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You head toward the exit\Nto keep a lookout in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki managed to put a transmitter on Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left information for us\Nin her final moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know that she's dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's arrived at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he inside or outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right behind you, Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His coat is bulletproof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on distancing yourself from Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went outside and ran to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, ma'am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Untie this for me! Also... a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Café LycoReco.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were alive, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that "oh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki! Takina has Jin in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to the platform in Tokyo Station\Nand find Matsushita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san, please give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki's safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's headed your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return immediately with Matsushita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm glad she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for Mizuki\Nand take the train back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Matsushita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's behind an AC condenser 15 meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Was there\Nsomewhere you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's coming for me, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He murdered my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt he'd try\Nand kill me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato! He shook Takina off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm in Japan,\Nhe's sure to try and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back to the café for now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take shelter and decide\Nwhat to do after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato! Get Matsushita-san to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here right away,\Nwhile Takina has his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true assignment is to have you kill Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the significance of that\Npendant around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been entrusted with a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki, please take Matsushita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must see that it's carried out\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, er... please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you could leave it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who took the lives of my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have done it myself back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years ago, when he killed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin would have been\Nworking with me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be the one to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the Alan Children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just why have you been granted life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully ponder that question!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I don't want to take other's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be a Lycoris...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to do work to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the person who gave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you... Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you... your life...\Nthe Alan Institute will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's book it before things get complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, for now let's go\Nsomewhere else and calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Matsushita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika! So those are your men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp shooting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who requested your services?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman came to see me\Ndirectly three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full payment upfront in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make it a habit to respect\Nmy clients' privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Matsushita's family\N20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika, what happened to that leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard back from the cleaners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ID'd him using fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terminally ill drug addict who disappeared\Nfrom his hospital ward two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he can't move\Nor speak on his own at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But he was talking with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a third party talking\Nwith you over the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A camera in his goggles,\Na remotely-operated wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a speaker for his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-san never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he try to make me kill someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The project making use of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid four containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything goes well,\Nand the other half's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes one of you, Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything he said, me being\Na good guide, was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he was lying\Nwhen he called you a good guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't hear a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The manga you brought me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The flower you gave me\Nthat I don't know the name of♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You're not here yet today?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫I am aware of an emotion never felt before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Tracing along a picture decorating the\Nwindow, I travel through space alone♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫That should have been enough♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If I were to grab your hand♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫This town that knows not of solitude♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Becomes one that I can\Nnever return to ever again♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You reached your hand out to me,\Nand a shadow is born from the light♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Sing for me to listen\Nthe continuation of this story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Take me to a star that I've never seen before♫
